    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know you mean well with the resilience stuff but it doesnt feel like i'm growing. it feels more like i'm just a ghost haunting my own life. like i'm just playing a part in a play that ended a long time ago. there's nothing left inside to actually \"grow.\" it's just... void.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
