    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just a phase or needing rest. it's that the person who was supposed to live this life is gone. why should the shell keep pretending? it feels so pointless to keep maintaining a body that's just a container for nothing. it's like holding onto a heavy, broken piece of furniture that no one needs anymore.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
